<section id="about" class="section-padding section-divider">
  <div class="section-container">
    <p class="label mb-6">About</p>

    <h2 class="section-title mb-5" style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem); line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.02em; max-width: 24ch;">
      The best design isn't about pixels — it's about people.
    </h2>

    <p class="body-text max-w-2xl mb-8" style="font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75;">
      With roots in Miami and a career spanning Shazam (Now part of Apple), Glint (Now part of Microsoft), and Docusign, I've shaped
      products used by millions. I lead with empathy, build with intention, and make room
      for people around me to grow.
    </p>

    <a href="/about" class="about-more-link">
      More about me
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-more-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: gap 0.15s, opacity 0.15s;
  }
  .about-more-link:hover {
    gap: 0.6rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
</style>
